                                Our prices are very flexible. It depends on the artist whose doing the work, but generally we charge $100/hour. For larger, more involved pieces there could be a design fee of $25/hour but this also depends on the artist. Pricing is decided before we begin. We do require a non-refundable deposit to do any design work or to book an appointment. All deposits are non-refundable.
