                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseSix" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                Yes, you can absolutely get a totally free tattoo. The two primary methods to get free ink are:
                                <br>
                                #1. Have a tattoo party. As the person inviting the other people you are the “Host” and your artwork and tattoo are totally free. How it works is really quite simple; you invite 4 of your friends to get tattoos. Each of their tattoos will cost about $75-$200 depending on the size and detail of the image. We try to meet with everyone before the party to get an idea what they want and get the artwork done before the party. The tattoo parties are held here in our shop, usually on Sundays. We have our own music or you can bring your CD’s or ipod playlists that plug right into our sound system. We also have wireless internet and access to quite a few good take-out restaurants right in our area. Everyone has had a great time at each of our previous tattoo parties and we look forward to having a great time with you and your friends.
                                <br>
                                #2. Tell people about us. Dragon Lily Tattoo loves referrals so much that we reward people for telling their friends about us. For every friend that gets a tattoo we will reward you with 20% of what that friend paid for their tattoo; so if they got a $200 tattoo we credit you with $40 towards your tattoo. Many people are using our referral system to build credit towards a sleeve or a large backpiece while others are using it to get a smaller one sitting tattoo…all for no money out of their pocket.
                            </div>
                        </div>
